2. Third-party / adapted components (NOT covered by the MIT grant above)
------------------------------------------------------------------------
The following components are ports or adaptations of pre-existing community
work and remain subject to their original authors' licenses and terms. They
are included here for interoperability and credit, not relicensed:

  - GMTool/        — adapted from Ice's "GM Tool" (Ultima Online community
                     script), ported to the ModernUO API.
  - JoekuToolbar/  — adapted from Joeku's "Toolbar" (Ultima Online community
                     script), ported to the ModernUO API.
  - Boss/ImportedAbilities*.cs — reimplement the mechanic *logic* of the
                     community "Custom Abilities 3.0" pack on top of this
                     project's own RFBossAbility framework.

If you are an author of the above and want attribution adjusted or content
removed, please open an issue.

------------------------------------------------------------------------
3. ModernUO
------------------------------------------------------------------------
This module builds against ModernUO (https://github.com/modernuo/ModernUO),
which is distributed under its own license in its own repository. ModernUO
is not included in or relicensed by this repository.
